                   , random
                   , crypto-random >= 0.0 && < 0.1
  Exposed-modules:   Crypto.Random.AESCtr
  Other-modules:     Crypto.Random.AESCtr.Internal
  ghc-options:       -Wall

  Build-Depends:   cipher-aes >= 0.2 && < 0.3

Benchmark bench-cprng-aes
